snippet.textDisplay: I once ran a one-shot where there was a bunch of mind-swapping hijinks going on with a bunch of random encounters where I would roll a monster and what creature that monster had been turned into. Twice I rolled goblins in the body of mice, and both times the party decided to take the mice with them, so once they destroyed the source of the mind-swapping, the guy who was holding the mice in their pocket had the pocket rip open and two goblins jump out. I had planned for these goblins to be super angry, but the party had treated them so kindly, the goblins just hugged them and swore their fealty.

first campaign for my newbie players:
make goblins cute, a witch sent the party to kill a hoard of goblins and along the way the party adopted one boblin the goblin. after killing all except boblin the goblin, the witch told them to hand boblin over and they had an emotional argument with eachother and ended up having boblin handed over and one of the players legit cried as i burned boblin the goblin, PLOT TWIST the witch was the BBEG and by killing that specific hoard the witch became invinsible.

second campaign with the same people:

after rescuing the 5 y.o.princess the goblin's kidnapping, the naive princess went back to the goblin and decided to forgive them by hugging the frail goblin, nobody questioned it, nobody wanted insight or investigation checks or anything, the players were all "aww" and the goblin STABS THE PRINCESS WITH A POISONOUS BLADE and everyone went "AAAAHHHHH"

ahh... the joy of being the DM

snippet.textDisplay:
(Background) I’m playing in a dnd game that I’ve
Started a couple of months ago I’ve managed to capture a goblin and convinced my party to have him tell us where his domain is we go over there after a few traps and one of my party members almost poisoned us due to not being able to make a good roll to get us some herbs and have the goblin find out that they were poisoned (May the lord bless the soul who we may call the dungeon master) so then I go out and manage to roll a little higher then needed and after that the goblin tells me to use magic to light a fire but my spells weren’t fire related (all the spells I had were mage hand,light,charm,summon a fiend I was going for a character who could get out of situations without blood nor gore) as you could tell it was a situation for my idea you’ll know what it is later so I come up with a plan I ask the dm if I was able to use light (my spell) so I wouldn’t have to use fiend for now he agrees if I roll high enough I roll high enough and we eat then a ask him a question if he wanted to join our party he agreed and we go to his cave and meet other goblins who couldn’t resist my imperfections and allow us threw them we make it to the bug bear I use charm although he is immune to it and shakes it off then the goblins take his side then as my partner starts swinging an axe around which I said not to do I try to talk it out with the goblin as I change his name to an insult after a while I convince him to help with the bugbear though the bugbear did not care and yeeeeeeeeeets him to the other side of the room the other two goblins had enough and helps us out then we defeat him and I look to see the heal spell I had was not there so I go ask the dm if he could allow it he does and I sleep while two party members are on the brink of death row I sleep like a baby and both die so I ask the dm if we could backtrack a little we are and I am lucky to get a nod then I don’t remember a little after but I healed both then have a entire goblin army my next step was as clear as daylight and couldn’t be easier it was look for a slave I go to the nearest town and take a roll to find a slave nat 20 but no the dm doesn’t allow my perverted skeam and said no

All I’m saying thank you for the advice
